<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Back</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css">
</head>
<body>
   
    <div class="nav">
        <img src="./assets/images/game_flex.png" alt="Game Flex Logo">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="workouts">Workouts</a>
        <a href="nutrition">Nutrition</a>
        <form action="/logout" method="post">
            <button type="submit" id="logout-btn" class="btn btn-moving-gradient btn-moving-gradient--blue">Logout</button>
    </div>

    <div class="main">
        <h1 class="workout-header">Back</h1>

        <div class="workout-card">
            <div class="workout-container">
            <div class="workout-title">Uncharted climbs</div>
            <div class="workout-button"><img src="./assets/images/psX_button.png"></div>
            <div class="reps">3 warmup sets of 10</div>
            <div class="workout-images">
                <img src="assets/images/drake.png">
                <img src="./assets/images/pull_up.png">
            </div>
            <div class="workout-description">
                <ul>
               <li>Begin by surveying your surroundings for a sturdy bar or ledge. This could be a pull-up bar, a tree branch, or a ledge in an abandoned temple.</li>
               <li>Stand under the bar, looking up as if you're about to leap across a chasm.</li>
               <li>Jump up and grab the bar with both hands, gripping it with an overhand grip (palms facing away from you), shoulder-width apart.</li>
               <li>Engage your back muscles and pull yourself up until your chin is level with the bar. Imagine you're scaling a cliff in search of hidden treasure.</li>
               <li>Hold at the top for a moment, savoring the view (or catching a quick breath if you’re in the heat of the moment).
                Slowly lower yourself back down.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="workout-comment">
                <p>"Oh man, I'm so tired of climbing $#%#”</p>

                <p id="quote">(Nathan Drake - Uncharted)</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="workout-card">
            <div class="workout-container">
            <div class="workout-title">Minecraft Rows</div>
            <div class="workout-button"><img src="./assets/images/up_key.png"></div>
            <div class="reps">3 sets of 20</div>
            <div class="workout-images">
                <img src="assets/images/minecraft.png">
                <img src="./assets/images/back_row.png">
            </div>
            <div class="workout-description">
                <ul>
                    <li>Mine and craft 5 Wooden Planks: These can be of any type (Oak, Spruce, Birch, Jungle, Acacia, Dark Oak).</li>
                    <li>Place the Wooden Planks in a crafting table in a row to create a Wooden boat.</li>
                    <li>Holding two blocks, pull blocks towards your waist, propelling you through a pixilated lake</li>
                    <li>Keep elbows close, and slowly return to starting position</li>
                    <li><span id='red'>Warning:</span> Creepers can swim!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="workout-comment">
                <p>"You can't expect to have diamonds without working hard and mining"</p>

                <p id="quote">Minecraft</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="workout-card">
            <div class="workout-container">
            <div class="workout-title">Bear Fling</div>
            <div class="workout-button"><img src="./assets/images/psSqr_button.png"> + <img src = "./assets/images/psTri_button.png"></div>
            <div class="reps">4 sets of 6-8</div>
            <div class="workout-images">
                <img src="./assets/videos/Untitled video.gif">
                <img src="./assets/images/barbell.gif">
            </div>
            <div class="workout-description">
                <ul>
                    <li>Ensure you're within range for a throw (Whiff punishes are embarassing)</li>
                    <li>Stand feet hip-width apart, claws pointing slightly outward</li>
                    <li>Wait for opponent to come within range, and pretend to grip a heavy barbell</li>
                    <li>Engage your back muscles and lift the barbell, launching opponent</li>
                    <li>Combo juggle, or simply return to starting position</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="workout-comment">
                <p>"Sorry, but human rules do not apply to bears."</p>

                <p id="quote">Kuma (Street Fighter X Tekken)</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>